					<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210805144102/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/1_Pet/8136?vers_inline=1"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210805144102im_/http://catholicbible.online/assets/img/para.jpg" alt=""/></a>					<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210805144102/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/1_Pet/8136?comments_open=1"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210805144102im_/http://catholicbible.online/assets/img/C-off.gif" alt=""/></a>				</div>
